<bibRefCitation author="Kazantsev, S. V." box="[384,575,1627,1653]" pageId="1" pageNumber="584" pagination="377 - 387" refId="ref4230" refString="Kazantsev, S. V. (2020) First fossil representative of the net-winged beetles genus Plateros Bourgeois, 1879 (Insecta: Coleoptera: Lycidae) from Mexican amber, with redescription of Electropteron avus gen. n., sp. n. from Dominican amber and a note on the time of origin of the family. Russian Entomological Journal, 29 (4), 377 - 387. https: // doi. org / 10.15298 / rusentj. 29.4.04" type="journal article" year="2020">Kazantsev, 2020</bibRefCitation>
